Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:04.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,（前情回顧）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:05.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,另一個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:13.46,Default2,,0,0,0,,(AV男優很努力的工作）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:18.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,（各種各樣的拍攝每天做愛）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.81,0:00:22.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,（像夢一樣過著充實的每一天）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:28.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,（突然某天RPG使其離開）\N（原本待的世界）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:32.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,（那裡是跟現實世界不一樣的世界）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:36.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,（這就是流行的異世界召喚嗎）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:12.46,Default2,,0,0,0,,（一切都是未知的開始了）\N（異世界生活）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:20.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,（突然來到了異世界）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:26.21,Default2,,0,0,0,,（突然被襲擊）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:31.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,（被追趕）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:37.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,（差點被殺死）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:43.50,Default2,,0,0,0,,（一開始不知道怎麼辦）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:48.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,（希望能少遇到點敵人）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:55.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,出現了\N（零零碎碎開始了生活）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:02:00.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,（出現了爆彈岩）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:05.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,出现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.36,0:02:07.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,还没发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:09.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:21.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,还是先观察一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:33.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,（因為很謹慎）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:34.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,雖然只能打倒弱小的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:40.41,Default2,,0,0,0,,（但是也在慢慢變強吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:47.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,（話说那時)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:52.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,（狼是勇者還是很吃驚的）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:57.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,（之後一直沒有看到）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:22.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:52.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,（狼三銑士出現了）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:58.22,Default2,,0,0,0,,不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:02.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,很厲害的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:05.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,但是我也變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:07.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:09.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,你這個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,打倒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:24.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,被打倒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:41.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:48.68,Default2,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:51.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,有可樂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:53.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,太好了\N（得到了可樂）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:35.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,（野生熊出現了）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:08.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,今天好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:15.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:16.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:18.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:25.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:44.59,Default2,,0,0,0,,我變強了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:56.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,應該可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:02.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:05.22,Default2,,0,0,0,,這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:12.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,不是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:15.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:21.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,喂 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:30.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,是哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:32.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:34.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:37.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:49.25,Default2,,0,0,0,,（盜賊A 盜賊B 出現了）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:53.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,是你們 之前襲擊我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:57.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,我的東西都被你們搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:00.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:04.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,還有一個只穿內褲的變態呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:08.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,大哥你說什麼呢 我們不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:13.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,不想受傷的話 就把東西乖乖\N給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:17.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,大哥啊 我們肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:20.16,Default2,,0,0,0,,給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:21.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:35.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,（跟那時不一樣）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:39.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,（變強的我不會再輸了）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:52.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,你很強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:12.67,Default2,,0,0,0,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:14.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:18.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,是你們突然襲擊我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:21.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:23.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,如果肚子餓的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:24.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,請吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:34.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:38.43,Default2,,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:46.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:53.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,吃了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:58.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:10:02.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,吃的這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:04.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:05.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:08.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:10.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,剛才不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:14.74,Default2,,0,0,0,,沒事 我沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:17.68,Default2,,0,0,0,,不好意思兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:28.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:34.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:44.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:50.71,Default2,,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:53.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,謝謝你讓我可門恢復體力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:11:01.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,現在能有力氣多虧了大哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:09.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,吃了你的食物今天起我們就是\N大哥的夥伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:11.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,夥伴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:14.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:16.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,以後多多關照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:22.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,你們突然這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:26.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,好為難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:28.68,Default2,,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:32.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,好好相處
