Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:44.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,（好為難啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:46.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:49.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:07.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:09.65,Default2,,0,0,0,,謝謝大哥
