Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:20.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:22.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:23.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,喂
